metadata.name: Shared Vision
metadata.description:
Artwork by Baked Papaya. 
Genesis of the TCH series.

This token is Your key into The Corner House, unlocking exclusive access to our album, future collaborations, and IRL/Meta events. 
We stand on the shoulders of our ancestors and community. That's why 10% of this token's primary sales will be used as our Community funds. These funds will A) provide food, supplies, and other resources to our local communities, South Los Angeles and Long Beach, 
B) introduce BIPOC and LGBTQ artists/creators/community builders into crypto.
